# Model Benchmarking on CUDA 12.8

This directory contains Docker configuration files for an image used for benchmarking deep learning models on CUDA 12.8 platforms.

## Directory Structure

*   `src/`: Contains configuration files and artifacts generated by `pei-docker-cli`.
*   `docs/`: Contains relevant documentation for using and maintaining this environment.
*   `memo/`: Contains notes and documentation generated during the development process.
